{
  "stem": "12053.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one thing I must tell you about that one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Shouldn't wash one's dirty linen in public, but although it was a Jewish school, we children who came from Polish extraction, meaning, although I was born in Germany, my parents were-- my mother was there since she was a baby.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father straight after the First World War, who he fought for Austria, Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He came from Galicia, Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mother was born in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when she was a little girl, she came with her family to Nuremberg, so which made us, actually, in the German mind, Polish-- from Polish extraction.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But not only in the German mind-- also among the Jews, there was a big division.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know if you know about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's rather sad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got very angry a few weeks ago.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two wonderful books came out-- I believe I showed you one before, which depicts the history of my family in great detail.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all the other people-- most of the other people it depicts, I know about myself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A few weeks ago-- and that's at the [GERMAN] in Munchen-- the East Jews, the Polish Jews in Munich.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I, well, I wasn't that happy with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But because my family appeared so-- and all my, my cousins and everybody is in there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I thought, well, that was the East German Jews in Munich.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few weeks ago, I was sent from Germany a wonderful book-- again, quite a heavy book.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it also said, But guess what?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those were the yekkes, the German Jews in Munich.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it-- I was so upset that, after 60 years, the division still seems to persist in some way, although it's watered down quite a lot.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in those days, they did not mix.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
